description:
Oatmega believes if you call something a cookie, it should actually taste like a cookie. With Oatmega Peanut Butter Cookie, you get the taste and experience of the soft, peanut-buttery cookie you crave, but with 13g of protein, 9g of fiber, and only 13g of sugar.
